    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>This recipe takes around 5-10 min to prep, so get your oven-proof dish and all your ingredients ready, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Make sure your dish is oven-proof and safe to use on the hob. Don't have one? Start cooking in a large, wide-based pan then transfer to an oven-proof dish and cover with tin foil</p>",
      "order": 1,
