      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> sweet potato[es]</strong> (skin on) into small bite-sized chunks</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1677669920273-x200.jpg",
