    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once your stew is ready, remove the dish from the oven and stir through the <strong>spinach</strong>, put the lid back on and let it stand for 2-3 min or until it has wilted – this is your <strong>one-pot Ethiopian-style free range chicken thigh stew</strong></p>",
